      ],
      "content": "For more information, see <bpt id=\"p1\">[</bpt>Configure AlwaysOn Availability Groups in Azure (GUI)<ept id=\"p1\">](virtual-machines-sql-server-alwayson-availability-groups-gui.md)</ept>."
    },
    {
      "content": "Availability group listener support",
